# Example trips file for UK ILR Absence Calculator
# Copy to trips.txt and edit with your actual travel dates

# Format: dep MM/DD/YY (departure) and arr MM/DD/YY (arrival)
# Only whole days abroad count - departure and arrival days are excluded

# Trip 1: Winter holiday
dep 12/20/24
arr 1/5/25

# Trip 2: Business trip
dep 3/10/25
arr 3/15/25

# Trip 3: Summer vacation
dep 7/1/25
arr 7/20/25

# Trip 4: Currently abroad (no arrival = open trip)
dep 11/15/25
